To solve this question you need to know DSU.Once you know how DSU works this question is a piece of cake.
If you don't know DSU you can think is as a black box which tells if the two elements are related and if related who is the ultimate parent of those two.
findUPar(): returns the ultimate parent of that element.
unionBySize(): merge the both elements and updates the ultimate parent according to specified condition
Use the DSU Template and Try solving it.
