s2[2] = 'r'

'r' == 'r' (No effect)

4. Index - 3
s1[3] = 'k'
s2[3] = 'r'

'k' == 'r' ('k' is lexicographically smaller than 'r')

Therefore, 'k' will be a parent of 'r'

   k
