# Intuition
In order to form a cycle 2 paths merge at a same node. This is the whole crux of the problem.
if a point is already visited and another path visits it again then there exist a cycle.

Points to be noted for algo
1. There are 4 directions possible to go from a cell. but we should not go to cell we have came from in a path.
2. Also go to only same character cells

# Approach
On the matrix
2. 1. In the grid start performing the BFS or DFS. if it is not visited.
2. perform this until you find a cycle or the 2d array is traversed completely.

 DFS:
see the code self explanatory

Inside BFS:
see the code self explanatory

